                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Dansent au cimetière entre les cyprès ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Tout un bruissement lointain de forêts",
